Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:38.99,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord0\c&H01006B&\fs45\fscx1000\pos(110.196,0.001)}▇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:38.99,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord0}目前可以公開的情報
